UNDOING THINGS:
Get old versions - git checkout [hash]
Return to latest version - git checkout [branch]
Undo local changes (before staging) - git checkout [file]
Undo staged changes (before committing) - git reset HEAD [file]
Undo committed changes - git revert [hash]
Remove commits from a branch - git reset --hard [hash]
Amend commits - git commit --amend
